ding_here_no_op + nums[i],  # Continue subarray without operation\n                nums[i]                           # Start new subarray without operation\n            )\n            \n            # Update the overall maximum sum found so far\n            max_so_far = max(max_so_far, max_ending_here_with_op)\n        \n        return max_so_far\n```\n\nThis solution uses dynamic programming to keep track of the maximum subarray sum both with and without performing the squaring operation. It iterates through the array, updating the maximum sums accordingly, and finally returns the maximum subarray sum that can be achieved with exactly one squaring operation.", "estimated_date": 1612051200000}